title: RHOBH Rosé & Chicken Salad, Girl
itunes:title: RHOBH Rosé & Chicken Salad, Girl
description:
Danny recaps The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills, which featured the Rinna Rosé launch that everyone is pretending we've been aware of for 3 years, plus Erika lets her dominatrix side come out, we spend time with Sutton's kids as she makes chicken salad, and lots more, girl.
